hopobject.body: Another year juntos feminine rejuvenation mg UrbanVeda is a brand new skincare range based on the ancient principles of Ayurveda. Originating 5000 years ago, Ayurveda’s holistic health and wellbeing system promotes the idea of using nature to live a healthier and more balanced lifestyle. Harmonising these principles in a relevant way for 21st century skin complaints, UrbanVeda is naturally formulated to ‘pollution-proof’ skin, helping to protect it from urban environmental pollutants which can combine to deplete the integrity of our skin. UrbanVeda are giving one lucky reader the opportunity to WIN a full hamper of products from the beautifully balancing ‘Purifying’ range which uses Ayurvedic Neem along with detoxifying botanicals to keep the complexion clear, cleanse and uplift the skin.
